reactivity-demo-shiny

The goal of this repository is to show how to implement a reactive data-science app using Shiny.

This is part of Data-Science Reactivity: Three Ways, an effort to show how to make the same app, using:

  • R: Shiny
  • Python: Dash
  • JavaScript: Observable

Aggregate: local

Theres a deployed version of this app.
